{"tid":701011,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"記低啱啱發生嘅夢境","createTime":"2018-06-13T20:20:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-13T22:34:52.000Z","uid":175523,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bd99b5f386281996422aaff64bbed171424b35d8","tid":701011,"uid":175523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T20:20:36.000Z","msg":"純粹想記低自己發過嘅夢<br />\n<br />\n淨係追溯到同三四個朋友行緊去食飯<br />\n大堂地下同牆淨係得白色，好白<br />\n吊燈係昏黃色，有兩部lift喺中央<br />\n成個空間感覺唔到邊界<br />\n<br />\n撞到現實入面嘅一位朋友<br />\n唔算好老友，搭咗枱，佢有啲驚喜<br />\n枱同凳都係好白嘅白色<br />\n張枱好大，無接駁位，一體<br />\n凳比較高身，中間係金屬管<br />\n記憶中我好似同左手邊嘅女仔傾咗陣偈<br />\n呢部分好模糊，已經對佢無晒印象<br />\n<br />\n之後離開，經過個大堂<br />\n發現自己行快咗<br />\n一回頭，佢哋個個都傾住偈咁行<br />\n得我自己一個喺前面，想行返過去<br />\n突然間好暈，全身無力，慢慢癱軟<br />\n迷糊中佢哋衝晒過來叫我<br />\n<br />\n醒返，感受到身邊電話喺到震<br />\n覺得係老豆打來<br />\n但係成身無力，好辛苦先撳咗個電話一下<br />\n出唔到聲，另一邊好似聽到佢鬧我<br />\n急住起身，唔小心跌咗落地<br />\n<br />\n醒返，現實過咗約莫半個鐘"},{"pid":"cb02eb444ad3b0e240da1a640cc8620a2199211f","tid":701011,"uid":179571,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T22:12:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c12e81a7db09d5679b139d8df3eeb9eea63ae7e9","tid":701011,"uid":2419,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T22:33:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcQN7wYZtxgWcCNTtLyyAbWlRIP8sHbMY7Z9pxGChrfFqqe38QA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%3AANd9GcQN7wYZtxgWcCNTtLyyAbWlRIP8sHbMY7Z9pxGChrfFqqe38QA&h=52e880a7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b95749e376556edf4abdf97ca88985fb04328c3a","tid":701011,"uid":171598,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T22:34:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/14/063434_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F14%2F063434_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=eeecb17d&s={SIZE}\" /><br 